column125:
I believe this Survey was Biased based off of my own decisions reflecting the Questions Relayed to me after.

I am generally completely neutral however these issues that I agree should be taken care of are commonly associated with one party over the other.

I However remain Politically neutral despite and individual beliefs I have that associate with either party.

I would also like to add that this Survey was of high quality and appreciate the effort dedicated to making it that way.

Have a great new year, and I would be honored to assist you via interview whenever the need arises.
